First one:

Hadoop depends on guava 11.0.2, and hadoop-aliyun uses *allAsList* interface which returns mutable list. However, when we run hive jobs on hadoop, it will throw ConcurrentModificationException because hive contains higher guava version and its *allAsList* interface returns immutable list.

 

Second one:

Stabilise the constructor of CredentialsProvider so that other developers can have their own implementations.
